import React from 'react'
import styled from 'styled-components'
import Navbar from '../components/Navbar'
import Announcement from '../components/Announcement'

const Container = styled.div``

const ProductList = () => {
  return (
    <Container>
      <Announcement />
      <Navbar />
      <title>Dresses</title>
      <FilterContainer>
        <Filter></Filter>
      </FilterContainer>
    </Container>
  )
}

export default ProductList
